nodes.text: The Return was a prophecy of the Keshiri. It described how a group of legendary Protectors would come to their homeworld of Kesh, and that the Destructors, who had previously ravaged Kesh would return and fight the Protectors. They believed that the Lost Tribe of Sith, who had crashed on Kesh, were the Protectors and that the Destructors had yet to return.
